:"text","text":": \"think\" (4K), \"think hard\" (10K), \"ultrathink\" (32K)"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The mental model: Think of the thinking budget as "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"allocating computational \"time\" for Claude to ponder"},{"type":"text","text":"—more time for harder problems, less for simpler ones, always balancing quality against cost/speed."}]}]}}
